                    The 1-to-1 Solution
                                                                                                       

   Key exchange rates, East German marks for West German
marks, under yesterday's compromise plan for German economic
reunification.
                                                                                                       

   1-to-1
                                                                                                       

   -- Wages and salaries
   -- Pensions
   -- Rents
   -- Personal savings up to 4,000 marks*
                                                                                                       

   2-to-1
                                                                                                       

   -- Company debts
   -- Personal savings above 4,000 marks*
   -- All other monetary exchanges
                                                                                                       

   *People 60 and older may exchange 6,000 marks in personal
savings at the 1-to-1 rate; those 14 or younger only 2,000
marks.
